These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, soy-milk
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | tea | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, western
1. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | western | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo, cycling
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Sport   | skateboarding | water-polo | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, hedgehog, hamster
1. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Pet   | turtle | hamster | hedgehog |

